collection of my vim configuration options and plugins in Ubuntu

Add the vimrc.local in /etc/vim folder

Add doc, ftplugin, nerdtree_plugin, plugin and syntax folders in yout home folder.
e.g.
/home/lfrsilva/doc
/home/lfrsilva/ftplugin
/home/lfrsilva/nerdtree_plugin
/home/lfrsilva/plugin
/home/lfrsilva/syntax
